ate-freedom/0000018e-ce80-df04-adae-efd2b8d70000</guid></item><item><title>说出第三种说法：10 月 7 日如何让这些巴以和平活动人士采取行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-october-7-jolted-these-palestinian-israeli-peace-activists-into-action/0000018e-c7a7-dc93-adce-eff74d5a0000</link><description>易卜拉欣·阿布·艾哈迈德和阿米拉·穆罕默德主持新播客“Unapologetic”，旨在扩大以色列境内寻求和平的巴勒斯坦人的声音。他们解释了为什么中东和平阵营需要更大的紧迫感</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 19:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-october-7-jolted-these-palestinian-israeli-peace-activists-into-action/0000018e-c7a7-dc93-adce-eff74d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>与阿塞拜疆的战略关系如何成为利伯曼家族的业务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-strategic-relations-with-azerbaijan-became-the-business-of-the-lieberman-family/0000018e-c7d7-dd23-a3cf-e7d728a00000</link><description>在阿维格多·利伯曼与巴库关系密切的背景下，他的儿子阿莫斯和科比成为阿塞拜疆政府和以色列科技公司之间的付费中间人</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 19:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-strategic-relations-with-azerbaijan-became-the-business-of-the-lieberman-family/0000018e-c7d7-dd23-a3cf-e7d728a00000</guid></item><item><title>“它是以色列的一部分”：与（极少数）梦想定居黎巴嫩南部的以色列人会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/part-of-eretz-israel-meet-the-very-few-israelis-dreaming-of-settling-south-lebanon/0000018e-cdbf-d5ed-adcf-ffbffe750000</link><description>称他们为极端分子中的极端分子：周三，一个规模虽小但充满激情的团体在海法附近集会，主张以色列通过占领黎巴嫩大片地区来确保其北部边境的安全。当被问及为什么这样的人这么少时，他们说，“只是没有人真正想到这一点”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 19:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/part-of-eretz-israel-meet-the-very-few-israelis-dreaming-of-settling-south-lebanon/0000018e-cdbf-d5ed-adcf-ffbffe750000</guid></item><item>