at/0000018e-cdab-dba9-a78e-efef6ba10000</link><description>战争的目标不会实现，人质不会通过军事压力返回，安全不会恢复，以色列的国际排斥不会结束</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 17:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/saying-what-cant-be-said-israel-has-been-defeated-a-total-defeat/0000018e-cdab-dba9-a78e-efef6ba10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 188 天：中央司令部司令在以色列会见以色列国防军司令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-188-centcom-commander-meets-with-idf-chief-in-israel/0000018e-cdef-df04-adae-edffb1b40001</link><description>美国高级官员告诉半岛电视台 如果德黑兰袭击以色列，美国不排除与以色列联合打击伊朗 ■ 美国中东特使要求沙特阿拉伯、阿联酋、卡塔尔和伊拉克外长敦促伊朗缓和与以色列的紧张局势 ■ “迫在眉睫的风险”华盛顿负责人道主义工作的特使称，“大多数加沙人正在遭受饥荒” ■ 以色列国防军称，哈马斯军事部门的主要财务人员被打死 ■ 以下是战争爆发 188 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 16:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-188-centcom-commander-meets-with-idf-chief-in-israel/0000018e-cdef-df04-adae-edffb1b40001</guid></item><item><title>特朗普、塔克和加沙战争：以色列正在失去共和党吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-11/ty-article/.highlight/trump-tucker-and-the-gaza-war-is-israel-losing-the-gop/0000018e-cdae-dba9-a78e-efeec0210000</link><description>众所周知，今天的共和党受到了两个人的启发：唐纳德·特朗普和塔克·卡尔森。 10 月 7 日后六个月，双方都公开反对以色列发动这场战争的方式</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 16:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-11/ty-article/.highlight/trump-tucker-and-the-gaza-war-is-israel-losing-the-gop/0000018e-cdae-dba9-a78e-efeec0210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队向加沙中部发动地面攻势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-launches-ground-offensive-in-central-gaza/0000018e-cdc6-dc93-adce-eff67a930000</link><description>空军和地面部队正在加沙中部努塞拉特难民营附近行动，预计行动将持续一周</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 16:32:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-launches-ground-offensive-in-central-gaza/0000018e-cdc6-dc93-adce-eff67a930000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡战争”如何导致民主党彻底重新思考美以关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/how-netanyahus-war-led-democrats-to-a-radical-rethink-of-u-s-israel-ties/0000018e-cd05-d5ed-adcf-ff9705150000</link><description>如果你六个月前告诉民主党议员查克·舒默和南希·佩洛西将带头呼吁以色列提前举行选举并限制军事援助，他们会质疑你的理智。但随后以色列与哈马斯的战争爆发了</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 16:30:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/how-netanyahus-war-led-democrats-to-a-radical-rethink-of-u-s-israel-ties/0000018e-cd05-d5ed-adcf-ff9705150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长发现没有法律依据阻止向以色列国防军征召犹太学院学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-finds-no-legal-basis-to-prevent-drafting-yeshiva-students-to-idf/0000018e-cd71-dce2-a1bf-cff70d470000</link><description>总检察长写道，政府必须在四月底之前向高等法院展示正在采取哪些措施将正统派纳入军队</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-finds-no-legal-basis-to-prevent-drafting-yeshiva-students-to-idf/0000018e-cd71-dce2-a1bf-cff70d470000</guid></item><item><title>我的女儿们不知道她们是犹太人，当然也不知道那有多危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-daughters-dont-know-theyre-jewish-and-certainly-not-how-dangerous-that-is/0000018e-c88a-d39c-a98e-dabb1fe40000</link><description>我们看地图，他们问那个小国家是什么。 “这是以色列，是你们出生的地方，”我告诉他们，也是我在美国学习后希望回到的地方。这里的每个人都走向了另一个方向</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 15:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-daughters-dont-know-theyre-jewish-and-certainly-not-how-dangerous-that-is/0000018e-c88a-d39c-a98e-dabb1fe40000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示以色列人对民主和国家安全未来的乐观态度创历史新低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-pessimistic-about-future-of-democracy-in-israel-poll-reveals/0000018e-cd51-dba9-a78e-ef5d1c250000</link><description>以色列民主研究所民意调查显示，以色列的国民情绪再创新低，35%的人表示对该国民主统治的未来持乐观态度，34%的人对国家安全持乐观态度</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 14:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-pessimistic-about-future-of-democracy-in-israel-poll-reveals/0000018e-cd51-dba9-a78e-ef5d1c250000</guid></item></channel></rss>